    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR1f0014-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-12T17:51:46.32+09:00">In ancient times, under conditions of supreme good order</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-12T17:53:09.644+09:00">those above and those shared one and the same virtue.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-12T18:16:06.63+09:00">To seek blessings from heaven</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-12T18:16:08.701+09:00">is the way of devotion.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_001-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-12T18:19:54.263+09:00">is nothing other than conformity with heaven.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-12T18:20:02.293+09:00">The nature of the way of devotion</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-12T18:23:09.699+09:00">rulers and subjects share one and the same virtue,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_001-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-12T18:26:12.119+09:00">then the cosmic energies of those blessings (of heaven) will definitely respond.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_002-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-12T18:33:05.533+09:00">It is the role of the ruler (of the world) to use the Virtue of the sages to survey the myriad lands.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_002-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-12T18:37:37.816+09:00">The sage ruler is above,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_002-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-12T18:38:58.274+09:00">and he applies his surveillance downwards to those below.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_002-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-12T18:39:31.559+09:00">The myriad lands are below,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_002-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-12T18:40:47.016+09:00">And the observation of performance has its proper place above.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_001-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-13T19:42:57.683+09:00">At the time when perfect order prevailed</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_001-5a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-13T20:48:00.946+09:00">                                    As for zhōng refers to concentrating the mind.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_002-6a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-13T20:58:23.305+09:00">                                    so as to cast glory on the ancestors,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_003-8a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-13T21:03:31.646+09:00">                                    and when the ministers are competent all business will be in peaceful balance.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_003-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-14T21:36:00.821+09:00">is the root of devotion.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_003-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-14T21:36:12+09:00">As a minister to serve (one's) ruler</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_003-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-14T21:39:30.715+09:00">Only when the root is established, will transformation be achieved.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_003-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-14T21:47:48.947+09:00">Even if one has the talent of a Duke of Zhōu or of Confucius,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_003-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-14T21:49:42.46+09:00">It is necessary to make devotion (one's) root.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_003-2a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-14T21:50:51.512+09:00">                                    because their sense of justice is the same</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_004-5a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-14T21:56:29.551+09:00">                                    If someone goes easy on himself and follows a devious course</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1f0014_tls_004-5a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="test" modified="2019-10-14T21:56:32.565+09:00">                                    then that is filling a position without doing the job. 尸位素食</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
